synopsis.text: The peaceful realm of Skyland is thrown into chaos when its young Princess El is kidnapped by a monstrous entity from the Underg Empire. A courageous girl named Sora, driven by her heroic aspirations, pursues the princess through a mysterious portal, only to find herself in an unfamiliar city known as Sorashido. In this new world filled with bewildering devices like televisions and cars, Sora encounters Mashiro, a junior high school student, and ends up residing with her and the kidnapped princess. Now, Sora must navigate this strange world and its advanced technologies to rescue the princess and restore peace to Skyland. The thrilling adventure of Pretty Cure begins, as Sora embarks on a journey between two worlds. It's time for heroes to rise!
